SEA 988 WHILST A LARGE REGION OF HIGH PRESSURE IS OVER THE MIDDLE OF THE
N ATLANTIC 1026. ON FRIDAY THE HIGH PRESSURE DRIFTS EWARDS TOWARDS SHANNON
