A SHALLOW TROUGH IS EXP TO MOV QCKY EWARDS AROUND THE N OF THE HIGH PRESSURE
CROSSING FM ICELAND TO NORWAY BETWEEN FRIDAY NIGHT AND SUNDAY MORNING BUT
